Title: I Asked ChatGPT to Run My Day – Here’s What Happened

Style: Voiceover / Faceless / Stock footage friendly

Length: ~5–6 minutes

Scene 1 – Hook
Text / Voiceover:
What if an AI decided how you spend your entire day?
Visual Suggestion:
Person looking at phone, thinking, slow zoom

Scene 2 – Experiment Intro
Text / Voiceover:
Today, I asked ChatGPT to run my whole day —
from morning routine to night.
Visual Suggestion:
AI interface / calendar / digital graphics

Scene 3 – Why I Tried This
Text / Voiceover:
No planning.
No overthinking.
Just following AI instructions and seeing what happens.
Visual Suggestion:
Minimal workspace, calm morning visuals

Scene 4 – Morning Routine
Text / Voiceover:
ChatGPT started my day with a simple morning routine.
Wake up on time.
No phone scrolling.
Light stretching and clear priorities.
Visual Suggestion:
Sunrise, stretching, making bed, journalism

Scene 5 – First Impression
Text / Voiceover:
Honestly, it felt calm.
Structured.
Less rushed than my usual mornings.
Visual Suggestion:
Relaxed coffee, window light

Scene 6 – Workday Begins
Text / Voiceover:
For work, ChatGPT broke my tasks into focused time blocks.
One task at a time.
No multitasking.
Visual Suggestion:
Laptop, focused work, typing

Scene 7 – Breaks & Balance
Text / Voiceover:
It even scheduled breaks —
something I usually ignore.
Visual Suggestion:
Short walk, stretching, tea break

Scene 8 – Midday Reality Check
Text / Voiceover:
At first, I wanted to skip the plan.
But sticking to it showed me how distracted I usually am.
Visual Suggestion:
Clock ticking, phone notifications fading

Scene 9 – Productivity Results
Text / Voiceover:
By afternoon, I had completed more than usual.
And surprisingly, I felt less tired.
Visual Suggestion:
Checklist getting completed, calm desk

Scene 10 – Challenges
Text / Voiceover:
The hardest part was letting go of control.
Following instructions — even when I disagreed.
Visual Suggestion:
Person hesitating, then refocusing

Scene 11 – End of the Day
Text / Voiceover:
ChatGPT even planned a proper evening wind-down.
No late work.
No endless scrolling.
Visual Suggestion:
Evening lights, relaxing at home

Scene 12 – Final Outcome
Text / Voiceover:
The result?
A productive day — without burnout.
Visual Suggestion:
Satisfied expression, clean workspace

Scene 13 – Honest Reflection
Text / Voiceover:
Will I let AI run my life forever?
Probably not.
Visual Suggestion:
